title: Zack Hemsey - The Way (Piano Cover)
description:
This is one of my favorite pieces of music of all time. The intensity, beat, instruments, everything is absolutely gorgeous. It is the definition of epicness. It's out there with pieces like Time from Inception, Duck Shoot from the Crown or any Two Step From Hell pieces really. Of course, since this is a highly instrumental and percussion driven piece, I took some liberties to make it sound a little better...cause otherwise it would have had to be me just banging on the piano.
Thanks a lot for the 400 subs, really appreciate it!
Please leave any suggestions in the comment section.
I do every arrangement by ear so no music sheets sorry.
Thanks a lot for watching :)
